data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home located in the sought after Hallsville ISD. With its adorable curb appeal, spacious interior, and a decent-sized yard, this house is perfect for creating lasting memories with loved ones. The open floor plan allows for seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it ideal for entertaining. The bedrooms provide a cozy retreat, and the two bathrooms offer convenience for the whole crew. Step outside to the backyard oasis, where you can relax, play, or even start a garden. Don't miss out on this delightful home!
